     H            Y.
     F** UTLR22 ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY- GET YYM# FOR MONTHEND JOB       *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)                                 *
     F*           05/18/2018                               *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR22'
     F*                    PARM           $YYM    3
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $YYM  :  3A YYM#
     F*   OUT $RTN  :  1A RETURN FLAG (Y=MONTH END, N=NOT)
     F******************************************************
     I* SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        9  100YY
     I                                       11  120MM
     I                                       13  140DD
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $YYM    3
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $YYM
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      * RETRIEVE SYSTEM TIME
     C                     TIME           WSDT
      * CHECK FIRST DAY OF MONTH?
     C           DD        IFEQ 01
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       $RTN
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE 'N'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      * GET LAST MONTH
     C           MM        SUB  1         L@MM    20
     C           L@MM      IFLE 0
     C                     Z-ADD12        L@MM
     C           YY        SUB  1         L@YY    20
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADDYY        L@YY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELL@YY      XYY     2
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 01
     C                     MOVE '1'       XM      1
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 02
     C                     MOVE '2'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 03
     C                     MOVE '3'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 04
     C                     MOVE '4'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 05
     C                     MOVE '5'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 06
     C                     MOVE '6'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 07
     C                     MOVE '7'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 08
     C                     MOVE '8'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 09
     C                     MOVE '9'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 10
     C                     MOVE 'A'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 11
     C                     MOVE 'B'       XM
     C           L@MM      WHEQ 12
     C                     MOVE 'C'       XM
     C                     ENDSL
      * SET PARAMETER
     C                     MOVELXYY       $YYM
     C                     MOVE XM        $YYM
      *
     C           ENDP      TAG
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
